&bull; Serve as the main client interface on projects, clarify strategic requirements, explain complex ideas clearly, and manage expectations<br />
&bull; Oversee multiple producers and interdisciplinary project teams as large as 15 people<br />
&bull; Lead and inspire teams by communicating a vision for the project as well as involving people at the optimal levels for project success and overall account utilization<br />
&bull; Lead meetings with senior clients, ensure that they meet the stated objectives and stay on agenda<br />
&bull; Ensure all deliverables are of the highest quality<br />
&bull; Work in an independent fashion, solve problems, make decisions, and communicate effectively in difficult situations<br />
&bull; Be a passionate about delivering the best creative, but find ways of producing it that does not jeopardize schedule and budget<br />
&bull; Play a dual role of client advocate and R/GA team advocate<br />
&bull; Assist in training of producers and associate producers on R/GA methodology and PM skills<br />
&bull; Participate in the development of new business</p>
