			<description><![CDATA[R/GA London
Resource Manager


Job Description
R/GA London is looking to hire a Resource Manager who will be responsible for increasing efficiency across a group of accounts through effective management of staff resourcing. Reporting directly to the Group Director, Production (LDN),and Director, Resource Management (NY) this person will fill an essential role in daily company operations through oversight of staff aggregate bandwidth, utilisation and realisation rates, retention/employee relations issues, ongoing matching of individual project needs with staff skill sets. Development of a nuanced understanding of creative and technical talents of numerous individual staff members will be critical, as well as an ability to serve as a sounding-board and source of confidence within a fast-paced group setting.

