<p>
<strong>Community Manager</strong><br />
The Community Manager is an appointed administrator for clients&rsquo; corporate social media communities: Facebook, Twitter and YouTube.&nbsp; The Community Manager is responsible for managing, creating, and moderating brand and UGC content for clients&rsquo; social communities.&nbsp; They will also assist in monitoring and reporting on industry and competitive trends, campaign initiatives and community optimization.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>Key Responsibilities: Community Strategy 15%</strong></p>
