</ul>
<br />
<p>
<strong>Management &amp; Moderation 75%<br />
<br />
<br />
Listening &amp; Reporting:</strong></p>
<br />
<ul>
<li>
Utilize social analytics tools like Facebook Insights, Radian 6 or Simply Measured to&nbsp;generate insights.</li>
<li>
Summarize insights and conversations to create actionable, client-facing reports that lead to optimization.</li>
</ul>
<br />
<p>
<strong>&nbsp;Publishing</strong></p>
<br />
<ul>
<li>
Create and maintain Content Calendars for all social communities, including writing Facebook Status Updates, Tweets and YouTube asset management.&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>
<li>
