He/she will be responsible for growing and developing the Mobile &amp; Social Platforms offering at R/GA London so he/she must be able to work closely with clients and collaborate effectively across all disciplines at R/GA London to bring to market effective and award-winning work.&nbsp; By working across the entire R/GA London office, the candidate will bring his/her mobile &amp; social expertise to the new business process, the strategic planning process, and the creative implementation process.&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;<br />
The candidate will work closely with R/GA London&rsquo;s leadership team and the SVP of Mobile &amp; Social Platforms in NYC to establish a R/GA London POV for mobile &amp; social, to establish office-wide best practices, and to continuously look to improve our mobile &amp; social capabilities in London.<br />
