<strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong><br />
<u>Support New Business 30%</u><br />
The ideal candidate will spend 30% of his/her time supporting the R/GA London new business process.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
<u>Account Support 50%</u><br />
Another 50% of the candidate&rsquo;s time will be spent focused on supporting accounts.&nbsp; The candidate will support/direct the creation, conception, and presentation of mobile and social work.&nbsp; He/she wil work to communicate and coordinate with client service, production, strategy/planning, and creative teams to ensure that the account&rsquo;s mobile and social work supports the clients&rsquo; overall brand goals and objectives.<br />
