Quality Assurance &amp; Release Manager - London<br />
London, UK<br />
<br />
The Quality Assurance &amp; Release Manager is responsible for testing and deployment across R/GA London projects.&nbsp;&nbsp; The role entails writing test plans, testing experiences across browsers, devices and installations, tracking defects, and deploying builds to staging and production environments.&nbsp;&nbsp; You work in collaboration with development and creative teams to communicate and document interaction and experience expectations, and to build testing into project schedules and scope.&nbsp; As the key advocate for QA, you participate in the execution of many high-profile projects across the office.</p>
