Position Summary:
 
A Learning and Development professional who will partner with the SVP of HR, HR Business Partners, the Executive team, and managers to align with business strategy, assess needs and requirements, and design and deliver solutions to inspire creative excellence and improve workplace performance. The position is based in New York City and reports to the Senior Vice President of Global Human Resources. The successful candidate must be able to operate in a fast-paced technologically and creatively driven environment.
 
