Ability to inspire team and manage careers

Exceptional communications skills, whether it be clients, peers or team

Attention to detail and accuracy

Ability to prioritize and organize large volumes of projects

Extensive client management and engagement experience




Qualifications:   
10+ years experience. Proven leadership across disciplines and channels in traditional and some digital agency exprience.



Able to mentor, counsel and lead the teams

Knowledge of Flash, Photoshop, InDesign, and Illustrator

Attention to detail and accuracy

Hands on writer or visual designer

Idea, big thinker in concepts



 
 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
