Creativity: An innovative and resourceful person who thinks and acts &ldquo;outside-of-thebox.&rdquo; This individual possesses a left brain/right brain mindset. Recreationally they are<br />
likely to most enjoy nurturing their creative passions and hobbies.</p>
<p>
Technology Forward: Has a passion for technology, tinkering under the hood, and enjoys being a sought after authority and the resource that others turn to for emerging media.</p>
