<li>
Ability to juggle multiple projects and to delegate work effectively.</li>
<li>
Mediation skills&mdash;necessary to maintain good team chemistry and client relations, and to sort out interpersonal conflicts as they arise.</li>
<li>
A strong desire to do brand-building, and award-winning work.</li>
<li>
An ability to discern individual team members&rsquo; abilities and to match the right people with the right work.</li>
<li>
Marketing sense &ndash; must possess an ability and an interest in helping to develop advertising campaign platforms that can work across channels, offline as well as online.</li>
<li>
PREVIOUS DIGITAL AGENCY EXPERIENCE IS REQUIRED</li>
