A Producer manages interactive projects from kick-off to delivery on time, on budget, and on brief. A Producer is everyone&rsquo;s point person for the project. Clients and internal team members rely on you for everything they need to know about a project: what to expect, what to do next, and where they need to be.</p>
<p>
Key Responsibilities/Accountabilities:</p>
<p>
