Brief Description<br />
The Group Account Director leads and manages client engagements and is responsible for the overall client satisfaction, quality of service, and on-time, on-budget completion of the agency&rsquo;s services. In terms of budget and staff under management, the position&rsquo;s responsibility is equivalent to managing a small agency. This position is a great opportunity for ambitious executives working in interactive media, communications, or advertising fields.<br />
Description<br />
