As a member of the executive team the role is to build, inspire and drive the profitable growth of a world-class, multi-disciplinary in-sourcing office, focused on digital delivery services for the rest of the R/GA network, including but not limited to: front-end technology solutions, back-end technology solutions, CMS and other technology and content platform maintenance and support, quality assurance testing, online advertising production, and visual asset production.&nbsp; This position will have the primary responsibility of the total profit and loss of the office, operations management including Romanian legal compliance, as well as management of R/GA network relationships, people management, and the quality of the work. The ability to collaborate, connect and engage with the different offices, disciplines, and account teams is critical.</p>
