R/GA develops award-winning digital strategies for the world&rsquo;s leading companies and brands. Sounds like a lot of work, right? It is. This is why we need fresh perspectives like yours. We work in an environment that embraces collaboration across all disciplines and encourages people to explore beyond the boundaries that limit visionary ideas. We&rsquo;re creating digital experiences for brands like Nike, Verizon, and Nokia that build communities and connect people globally. As an intern, you&rsquo;ll work side-by-side with our industry&rsquo;s brightest minds&mdash;receiving mentorship, training, and experience on real, live accounts. You&rsquo;ll also take part in seminars, panels, and projects that will connect you with the latest industry trends and information. In short, you won&rsquo;t be bored. So if you&rsquo;re passionate about mapping the digital landscape as it evolves; and aspire to become a best in class designer, copywriter, technologist, producer, data intelligence specialist, client services liaison, or strategic planner; please apply for an internship at R/GA. We&rsquo;d love to hear from you.</p>
