<strong>Summary of Position</strong><br />
We seek an entrepreneurial professional to help build the new Brand Consulting practice at R/GA. This practice will redefine how brands transform businesses within the context of the digital age.&nbsp; This person will assess consumer behaviors, business structures, market conditions and general trends to create opportunities for brands within our existing client engagements as well as new client opportunities. These are specific opportunities for evolution, adaptation, change and growth, and a brand strategy will serve as the foundational vehicle. This role will work collaboratively with the Product innovation and Consulting practices, and partner with various disciplines within the agency.</p>
